    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. The interior is equally immaculate, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls, displays, and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all mechanical systems in excellent working order and full service history available. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and shows virtually no signs of wear \u2014 a true turn-key purchase for a discerning buyer.",
