      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you consider making a purchase. The exterior shows visible wear consistent with regular use \u2014 you can expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas. The interior has seen its share of daily driving, with noticeable wear on the seats, dashboard trim, and carpeting. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention to bring it fully up to par \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a practical, functional vehicle suited for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. What you see is what you get, and we're committed to full transparency.",
