    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Mint condition gem right here \u2014 and we mean it! This beauty is in absolutely pristine shape from bumper to bumper. The exterior boasts a flawless, gleaming finish with zero scratches, dents, or blemishes \u2014 it truly looks showroom-fresh. Step inside and you'll find an immaculate interior with no wear, stains, or odors \u2014 just clean, well-kept perfection. Under the hood, everything is running smoothly and mechanically sound. If you've been searching for a vehicle that feels like new without the new-car price tag, this is your chance. Don't let this one slip away!",
