      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. This is a truly exceptional used car that presents and performs like new in virtually every respect. The exterior is flawless: the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with no visible scratches, chips, dents, or blemishes of any kind. All body panels align perfectly, trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is clear and undamaged. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show no signs of wear, fading, or staining. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended, from the infotainment system to the climate controls and power accessories. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service records are up to date, and the mechanical systems are in excellent working order. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that genuinely rivals a new one in condition and presentation. Ideal for a buyer who demands the best without paying new-car prices.",
